Q: Is &#8220;not being here now&#8221; the only thing that separates us from kaivalya (liberation)?
<br>A: &#8220;Here now&#8221; is a state of duality.
<br>Q: Is trying to &#8220;be here now&#8221; helpful, something we should cultivate?
<br>A: It&#8217;s still within time and space. <span class=date>7/13/80</span>
